Package: csviSubtype
Title: GWAS-Anchored Vascular-Centered Molecular Subtype Barcode Discovery
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Yuqian",
           family = "Li",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "yuqian-li@hotmail.com")
Description: 
    csviSubtype implements a GWAS-anchored and vascular-centered framework
    for molecular subtype barcode discovery. The package provides functions
    for building scRNA-derived feature scores, ranking subtype-relevant genes,
    fusing human genetic and single-cell evidence, and summarizing robustness
    under ablation settings.
